    "Some of the mechanisms through IoT to improve agriculture efficiency are discussed below:",
    "Real-time crop planning and Harvesting The IoT plays a crucial role in enhancing agricultural efficiency.",
    "It achieves this by monitoring the health and growth of crops and predicting their yield.",
    "IoT-enabled sensors, such as drones and satellite images, enable farmers to monitor the well-being of their crops.",
    "This allows them to identify issues, such as diseases or pests, at an early stage and provide targeted treatments."
